si.ijs.kt.clus.util.tools.optimization

Class OptProbl.OptParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • si.ijs.kt.clus.util.tools.optimization.OptProbl.OptParam
  • Enclosing class:
    OptProbl

    public static class OptProbl.OptParam
extends java.lang.Object
    Parameters for optimization algorithm. Predictions for rules and other base function and true values for all the instances of data. The default prediction is used, if no other rule covers the instance. See m_RulePred and m_TrueVal for what the indices mean.
